      • isComplexFormat

        public java.lang.Boolean isComplexFormat()
        Deprecated. 
        Description copied from interface: JxlReportConfiguration
        Flag specifying whether the cell format pattern is user-defined. When set to true, the exporter will assume that the specified pattern is well defined. If the pattern is invalid, it won't be taken into account by the Excel file viewer.
        Specified by:
        isComplexFormat in interface JxlReportConfiguration
        See Also:
        JxlReportConfiguration.PROPERTY_COMPLEX_FORMAT
